00:16:04,240 --> 00:16:05,960
So, tell the leader not to worry, okay?

302
00:16:05,960 --> 00:16:06,800
Alright.

303
00:16:06,800 --> 00:16:08,380
(Shuoyang Public Security Bureau)

304
00:16:08,790 --> 00:16:09,680
We need to locate

