00:16:17,790 --> 00:16:18,630
No place unchecked.

312
00:16:19,240 --> 00:16:20,930
Gather more men and expand the search area.

313
00:16:22,030 --> 00:16:23,760
Xiaoxing, go to the archives

314
00:16:23,770 --> 00:16:24,910
to check the missing persons

315
00:16:24,940 --> 00:16:25,960
from the past three months

316
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:27,240
