00:16:51,480 --> 00:16:52,320
He gave me one tablet

325
00:16:52,330 --> 00:16:53,320
and told me to take half,

326
00:16:53,320 --> 00:16:54,870
but I took the whole thing.

327
00:16:54,870 --> 00:16:56,080
I just couldn't wake up.

328
00:16:57,270 --> 00:16:58,440
You guys are fast, huh?

329
00:16:58,460 --> 00:16:59,340
Got your spot already.

330
00:16:59,350 --> 00:17:00,560
Yeah, we have.

331
00:17:01,790 --> 00:17:02,840
It's spacious.

332
00:17:05,790 --> 00:17:06,750
Where's mine?

333
00:17:07,400 --> 00:17:08,310
You're the captain.

334
00:17:08,310 --> 00:17:09,240
You oversee everything.

335
00:17:09,640 --> 00:17:10,480
Upstairs.

336
00:17:11,110 --> 00:17:12,310
Got an office upstairs?

337
00:17:13,110 --> 00:17:13,960
Alright.

338
00:17:13,960 --> 00:17:15,070
Guess I'll take it.

339
00:17:17,440 --> 00:17:18,310
Gao, what's up?

340
00:17:18,310 --> 00:17:19,960
You moved offices and didn't even tell me.

341
00:17:19,960 --> 00:17:20,800
Made me waste a trip.

342
00:17:21,160 --> 00:17:22,000
That's right.

343
00:17:22,480 --> 00:17:23,490
We moved to a new office.

344
00:17:23,720 --> 00:17:24,560
What's up?

345
00:17:24,790 --> 00:17:26,200
