346
00:17:26,440 --> 00:17:27,840
Matches your assessment exactly.

347
00:17:28,400 --> 00:17:29,960
I have late-stage colon cancer.

348
00:17:30,510 --> 00:17:31,480
The doctor said

349
00:17:32,030 --> 00:17:33,720
