400
00:20:17,240 --> 00:20:18,200
Found other torso parts?

401
00:20:18,200 --> 00:20:19,040
Not yet.

402
00:20:20,240 --> 00:20:21,920
Any info on the missing person?

403
00:20:22,160 --> 00:20:23,000
Nothing.

404
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:36,250
