00:21:00,160 --> 00:21:01,000
Yes.

412
00:21:02,310 --> 00:21:03,510
Where was the incident site?

413
00:21:04,160 --> 00:21:05,000
The sewer.

414
00:21:06,960 --> 00:21:08,180
You only found the right parts,

415
00:21:08,200 --> 00:21:09,040
right?

416
00:21:09,550 --> 00:21:10,390
Yes.

