458
00:22:28,480 --> 00:22:29,920
were made before death.

459
00:22:34,720 --> 00:22:35,560
Mr. Lin,

460
00:22:36,640 --> 00:22:37,790
we're working

461
00:22:37,790 --> 00:22:39,160
on a heinous case here.

462
00:22:39,720 --> 00:22:41,750
It's not about Yin-Yang
and Five Elements stuff

463
00:22:42,240 --> 00:22:43,240
you're talking about.

464
00:22:43,920 --> 00:22:46,000
Captain Xu, you're missing my point.

465
00:22:49,940 --> 00:22:51,750
Maybe we're approaching this differently.

466
00:22:51,910 --> 00:22:53,390
I just wanted to offer some advice.

467
00:22:53,550 --> 00:22:55,030
Well, thank you for the advice.

468
00:22:55,030 --> 00:22:56,240
But as you said earlier,

469
00:22:56,880 --> 00:22:57,750
our approaches

470
00:22:57,750 --> 00:22:58,710
