496
00:24:14,830 --> 00:24:15,670
Hold on.

497
00:24:21,510 --> 00:24:23,000
Let's go check the site again.

498
00:24:23,920 --> 00:24:24,760
Alright.

499
00:25:32,750 --> 00:25:33,720
Be careful.

500
00:25:56,110 --> 00:25:57,030
Inform everyone

501
00:25:58,590 --> 00:25:59,750
