504
00:26:02,030 --> 00:26:02,870
Got it.

505
00:26:05,030 --> 00:26:05,870
Captain Xu.

506
00:26:06,750 --> 00:26:07,750
It's been two days.

507
00:26:08,440 --> 00:26:09,750
