538
00:28:00,680 --> 00:28:02,000
Change out of the dirty clothes.

539
00:28:02,110 --> 00:28:03,160
Toss them into the washer.

540
00:28:03,160 --> 00:28:04,000
Okay.

541
00:28:04,640 --> 00:28:05,720
Easy on the drinks, alright?

542
00:28:06,030 --> 00:28:07,720
